  "id": "RAW_f8426dc3",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-11-19）：何恺明团队新力作！JiT 极简 PyTorch 实现高分辨率图像扩散生成，解锁像素级图像生成新范式",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500484&idx=1&sn=38f994aed760bf7329cc7bdf1f6c9312",
  "date": "2025-11-19 09:18:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">①项目：JiT</span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"620\" data-imgfileid=\"100016814\" data-ratio=\"0.5314814814814814\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=70d849fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzkPwXXzaLWwFLw33v7AkjRgk0bqaOZ0L1yBmCwKNMRJOFklzJreN7jzjaEH2E17pBicib0svDqPDDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★JiT 是一个基于 PyTorch 的高分辨率图像扩散模型的实现，旨在通过去噪生成模型进行像素级图像生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目最初在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;JAX+TPU</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;上实现，现已移植到 PyTorch+GPU 环境中。JiT 采用极简和自包含的设计，适用于高分辨率图像的生成任务。项目由ResNet 之父，超70万引用的 AI 大神何恺明团队开发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/jit\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/jit</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">②项目：BraInCoRL</span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"590\" data-imgfileid=\"100016813\" data-ratio=\"0.5055555555555555\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3821cb02&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzkPwXXzaLWwFLw33v7AkjR94sI2fC1SRFD0SSMWhxI3tkzaTxOplUL8tBrSC9vzode6WG8FaFp8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★BraInCoRL项目旨在通过元学习方法开发一个基于变压器的视觉皮层编码器模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型能够在无需微调的情况下适应新的个体和刺激，解决了传统方法在数据获取上昂贵且耗时的问题。BraInCoRL通过在上下文中学习，利用少量样本预测体素级神经响应，并在训练过程中优化模型以适应不同的上下文。该模型在低数据环境下对全新图像的表现优于现有设计，并能推广到使用不同受试者和fMRI数据采集参数的新数据集。此外，BraInCoRL还提高了对高阶视觉皮层神经信号的可解释性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/braincorl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/braincorl</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">①项目：LoopTool</span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"420\" data-imgfileid=\"100016811\" data-ratio=\"0.3592592592592593\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a300bf8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzkPwXXzaLWwFLw33v7AkjRcAVkdCcL8QFic7RXwQfSQjv4kJBpdqmiaNbUou2zd9S0kTzARq8wActQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LoopTool 是一个旨在增强大型语言模型（LLMs）工具使用能力的自动化数据进化框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过将数据合成与模型训练紧密结合，LoopTool 通过三个协同模块迭代地优化数据和模型：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">贪婪能力探测（GCP）、判断引导标签验证（JGLV）和错误驱动数据扩展（EDDE）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该框架在开源生态系统中运行，避免了对昂贵的闭源 API 的依赖。实验表明，使用 LoopTool 训练的 8B 模型在 BFCL-v3 和 ACEBench 基准测试中表现优异，显著超越了其 32B 数据生成器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/looptool\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/looptool</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">②项目：ConsistEdit_Code</span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"850\" data-imgfileid=\"100016812\" data-ratio=\"0.7305555555555555\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f2daa717&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzkPwXXzaLWwFLw33v7AkjR2NqjFib7yaSK9Qw1wsOmtPpiaichvWBXzdLMLISDibNn04CoxkM0LJUMPQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ConsistEdit是一个无需训练的视觉编辑项目，旨在提供高一致性和精确的图像编辑功能。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目由香港科技大学、清华大学和IDEA研究院的研究人员合作开发，计划在2025年SIGGRAPH Asia会议上展示。ConsistEdit利用多种扩散模型，包括Stable Diffusion 3、FLUX和CogVideoX-2b，支持颜色、材质、风格和对象的编辑。用户可以通过简单的脚本和命令行参数实现图像的快速编辑和合成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/consistedit-code\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/consistedit-code</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">③项目：EnchTable</span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4203703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" data-height=\"490\" data-imgfileid=\"100016810\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0955c8ac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzkPwXXzaLWwFLw33v7AkjRbpmPdBniasMGSNNaGbhAlPGcTrWvfdzLH0zIQ0jtgyAn7sJbIU0Qglg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★EnchTable是一个统一框架，旨在将安全对齐转移到微调的大型语言模型中，而无需进行广泛的再训练。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目结合了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">基于NTK的安全向量蒸馏</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">以提取安全知识，并采用干扰感知的合并策略以同时保留安全性和实用性。通过在不同模型和任务上的评估，EnchTable有效地减轻了微调过程中的安全性下降，保持了高任务性能，并在面对鲍鱼攻击时表现出强大的鲁棒性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/enchtable\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/enchtable</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">①项目：AgentEvolver</span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22407407407407406\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"260\" data-imgfileid=\"100016815\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=785fa355&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzkPwXXzaLWwFLw33v7AkjRcibomMMkOqHwCWGwUJTwA53y97fdoNlf3fBS3akHSJbHhHiaeX1OdyVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AgentEvolver是一个端到端的自我进化训练框架，将自我质疑、自我导航和自我归因整合为一个统一的系统。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目旨在通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">自动化任务生成、经验引导的探索和基于归因的信用分配</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，提升Agent的自主能力，实现高效、经济且持续的能力进化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/agentevolver\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/agentevolver</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总介绍了何恺明团队的 JiT 图像扩散模型、BraInCoRL 视觉皮层编码器等多个前沿 AI 开源项目，涵盖图像生成、LLM 工具增强和 Agent 进化等领域。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总介绍了何恺明团队的 JiT 图像扩散模型、BraInCoRL 视觉皮层编码器等多个前沿 AI 开源项目，涵盖图像生成、LLM 工具增强和 Agent 进化等领域。",
  "summary": "本文作为一篇“今日开源”的综述性文章，集中介绍了六个最新的 AI 开源项目，旨在帮助读者快速了解当前 AI 领域的前沿进展。其中，由何恺明团队开发的 JiT 项目，提供了高分辨率图像扩散模型的 PyTorch 实现，专注于像素级图像生成。BraInCoRL 则是一个基于元学习的视觉皮层编码器模型，能在低数据环境下适应新个体和刺激。此外，文章还涵盖了提升 LLM 工具使用能力的 LoopTool 框架，无需训练的 ConsistEdit 视觉编辑项目，用于安全对齐 LLM 的 EnchTable 框架，以及端到端自我进化的 AgentEvolver 训练框架。这些项目共同展示了 AI 在图像生成、模型训练、Agent 开发等多个子领域的最新突破和应用潜力，为技术从业者提供了丰富的探索方向。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "何恺明团队的 JiT 项目实现了高分辨率图像的像素级扩散生成",
      "explanation": "JiT 将原 JAX+TPU 实现移植到 PyTorch+GPU，以极简设计支持高分辨率图像生成，为视觉内容创作提供新工具。"
    },
    {
      "point": "BraInCoRL 通过元学习开发视觉皮层编码器，无需微调适应新个体和刺激",
